Package org.eclipse.graphiti.platform.ga

Interface IGraphicsAlgorithmRenderer

public interface IGraphicsAlgorithmRenderer
The Interface IGraphicsAlgorithmRenderer. A marker interface enabling the framework to distinguish between customer draw 2d figures and draw 2d figures created by the framework based on the Graphiti model. If a user of Graphiti needs to display custom draw 2d figures these figures need to implement this interface.
